  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/7684f27c425fe8c2dc592098b6f393ef.avif?t=1773846265\" width=600 height=143 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/dea3d756cc1b99e702aed2ffd6efc218.poster.avif?t=1773846265\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/dea3d756cc1b99e702aed2ffd6efc218.webm?t=1773846265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/dea3d756cc1b99e702aed2ffd6efc218.mp4?t=1773846265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>STUFFED is a procedurally generated, horde first-person shooter, that takes place in the dreams of a little girl. Play as a teddy bear and fight waves of nightmares as you defend your owner. Play solo or join your friends in up to 4 player online co-op.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/905717dca417b01a242dfb1f25c7a81a.poster.avif?t=1773846265\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/905717dca417b01a242dfb1f25c7a81a.webm?t=1773846265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/905717dca417b01a242dfb1f25c7a81a.mp4?t=1773846265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Defend your owner's bedroom door and defeat a variety of nightmares in endless waves. Earn points from defeating nightmares and use them to unlock new map areas and weapons.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/e46355a64e52a722bdfacb1d8c27607b.poster.avif?t=1773846265\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/e46355a64e52a722bdfacb1d8c27607b.webm?t=1773846265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/e46355a64e52a722bdfacb1d8c27607b.mp4?t=1773846265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>From a popcorn grenade to a jelly bean shotgun, find and use unique weapons made from household objects.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/d7d30f0a5a180a44480f7ef50f9a0d1f.poster.avif?t=1773846265\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/d7d30f0a5a180a44480f7ef50f9a0d1f.webm?t=1773846265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/d7d30f0a5a180a44480f7ef50f9a0d1f.mp4?t=1773846265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Earn XP in to unlock special player abilities each game session.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/8e3ff42e6b114cb5704e3c479dec0991.poster.avif?t=1773846265\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/8e3ff42e6b114cb5704e3c479dec0991.webm?t=1773846265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243200/extras/8e3ff42e6b114cb5704e3c479dec0991.mp4?t=1773846265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use points to unlock new outfits and furs for your teddy bear. Mix and match outfits and furs to fully personalise them.",
